rows.label: qev010802_MSG0001
rows.name:
Carl to field team. Come in, field team...
Yo, how goes? You find those beasties yet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev010802_MSG0002
rows.name: ...What? There's a bunch of young ones in the cave?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev010802_MSG0003
rows.name:
Well, damn. I don't want to tell anyone they've got to
go blast piglets. Even if they're monster piglets.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev010802_MSG0004
rows.name:
Though I guess that's the Interceptor way, right?
Secure mankind's safety, no matter the target?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev010802_MSG0005
rows.name:
Yeah, that's a real moral conundrum there.
But you're the one who has to live with it,
so I'm gonna leave it up to you. Over and out.[ST:wait ]
